Additional finding on second pass:

### D18 (new): "Linear, Notion, Figma" comparison contradicts deployment model

product.md:287 — "**iroum-ax 포지셔닝**: 수평적 플랫폼이 아닌 수직적 도메인 솔루션 (Linear, Notion, Figma 모델)".

These three are cloud-native SaaS companies. iroum-ax is self-hosted on-prem K8s targeting 망분리. The "model" being borrowed is unspecified — anchor-customer strategy? PLG? Vertical depth? Without clarification, this comparison misleads.

