1. Strip all calendar quarters/years and duration phrases (D1).
2. Replace emoji ⭐ ratings with text scale (D2).
3. Remove or relocate executable code blocks; keep schemas as design artifacts only (D3).
4. Reconcile embedding dimension: pick one and propagate (D4).
5. Reconcile Phase numbering between product.md and structure.md (D5).
6. Either add `task.proto` to the schemas listing or remove the reference (D6).
7. Consolidate SQL schema ownership (D7, decide between structure.md §5 / tech.md §9.3 / `.moai/project/db/`).
8. Pick a single Go control-plane layout (D8); fix the `pkg/` mixed-language layout (D9).
9. Tag every numeric KPI as "proposed, pending PoC measurement" or remove (D10).
10. Reword LG partnership claims as hypothesis until contract exists (D11).
11. Correct EXAONE size list and Llama 3.2 license (D12, D13).
12. Add "Decisions pending before SPEC-AX-001" section linking each TBD to a resolution owner (D14).
13. Disambiguate PoC vs. Go-Live (D15).
14. Surface load-bearing assumptions and fix the misleading Linear/Notion/Figma analogy (D16, D18).
15. Define explicit phase-entry gates rather than time-implied transitions (D17).

This document is not ready for SPEC-AX-001 derivation. Revision iteration 2 is required.
